headline: Wynn Resorts Set to Acquire Crown London From Crown Resorts
summary: LAS VEGAS, January 10, 2025--Wynn Resorts today announced that it will acquire Crown London (Aspinalls), a small, members-only casino in the heart of London's upscale Mayfair district. The acquisition is subject to the receipt of customary regulatory approvals, which are anticipated in the second half of 2025.
